        "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThis PR addresses issue #421 by optimizing the CSS to reduce the framework size while maintaining full compatibility. The goal was to style with fewer selectors and properties to get closer to the 2KB target.\r\n\r\n**Changes Implemented:**\r\n\r\n*   **Optimized Form Selectors ([src/_Form.sass](cci:7://file:///Users/apple/Downloads/milligram/src/_Form.sass:0:0-0:0))**: Refactored input selectors from a long whitelist to a concise blacklist using negation. This significantly reduces selector count and file size, and improves progressive enhancement.\r\n*   **Optimized Grid System ([src/_Grid.sass](cci:7://file:///Users/apple/Downloads/milligram/src/_Grid.sass:0:0-0:0))**: Removed redundant `column-34` and `column-67` classes (aliases for 33/66) and redundant properties from `.column`.\r\n*   **Optimized Base Styles ([src/_Base.sass](cci:7://file:///Users/apple/Downloads/milligram/src/_Base.sass:0:0-0:0))**: Removed negligible `letter-spacing` from `body`.\r\n*   **Build System Update**: Switched from deprecated `node-sass` to [sass](cci:7://file:///Users/apple/Downloads/milligram/src/_Grid.sass:0:0-0:0) (Dart Sass) to fix build issues.\r\n\r\n**Results:**\r\n*   **Baseline Size (Gzipped)**: 2274 bytes\r\n*   **Optimized Size (Gzipped)**: 2136 bytes\r\n*   **Total Reduction**: ~138 bytes (~6%)\r\n\r\n### Code sample\r\n\r\nThe usage of the framework remains exactly the same; these are internal optimizations to reduce file size.\r\n\r\n**Optimization Example (`_Form.sass`):**\r\n\r\n```sass\r\n// Before (Whitelist)\r\ninput[type='color'],\r\ninput[type='date'],\r\n// ... (many more)\r\nselect\r\n  // styles...\r\n\r\n// After (Blacklist)\r\ninput:not([type='button'], [type='checkbox'], [type='file'], [type='radio'], [type='range'], [type='reset'], [type='submit']),\r\ntextarea,\r\nselect\r\n  // styles...",
